agentSSLAdminMode.name: agentSSLAdminMode
agentSSLAdminMode.description: Configures whether the SSL service is enabled on this switch. The default value is disable(2).

agentSSLSecurePort.name: agentSSLSecurePort
agentSSLSecurePort.description: Configures the port the SSL service will respond on. The default value is 443.

agentSSLProtocolLevel.name: agentSSLProtocolLevel
agentSSLProtocolLevel.description: Configures which protocol versions of SSL are enabled on this switch. The default value is both(3).

agentSSLMaxSessions.name: agentSSLMaxSessions
agentSSLMaxSessions.description: Configures the maximum number of allowable SSL sessions. The default value is 16.

agentSSLHardTimeout.name: agentSSLHardTimeout
agentSSLHardTimeout.description: Configures the hard timeout for SSL sessions in hours. The default value is 24 hours.

agentSSLSoftTimeout.name: agentSSLSoftTimeout
agentSSLSoftTimeout.description: Configures the soft (activity) timeout for SSL sessions in minutes. The default value is 5 minutes.

agentSSLCertificatePresent.name: agentSSLCertificatePresent
agentSSLCertificatePresent.description: Boolean value indicating whether SSL certificate files exist on the device.

agentSSLCertificateControl.name: agentSSLCertificateControl
agentSSLCertificateControl.description: Controls certificate generation and deletion. Always returns noop(1).

agentSSLCertificateGenerationStatus.name: agentSSLCertificateGenerationStatus
agentSSLCertificateGenerationStatus.description: Indicates whether certificate files are currently being generated.

agentSSHAdminMode.name: agentSSHAdminMode
agentSSHAdminMode.description: Configures whether the SSH service is enabled on this switch. The default value is disable(2).

agentSSHProtocolLevel.name: agentSSHProtocolLevel
agentSSHProtocolLevel.description: Configures which protocol versions of SSH are enabled on this switch. The default value is both(3).

agentSSHSessionsCount.name: agentSSHSessionsCount
agentSSHSessionsCount.description: Current number of active SSH sessions on this switch.

agentSSHMaxSessionsCount.name: agentSSHMaxSessionsCount
agentSSHMaxSessionsCount.description: Max number of SSH sessions permitted on this switch.

agentSSHSessionTimeout.name: agentSSHSessionTimeout
agentSSHSessionTimeout.description: ssh idle timeout value for this switch im minutes.

agentSSHKeysPresent.name: agentSSHKeysPresent
agentSSHKeysPresent.description: Indicates what key files are present on the device, if any.

agentSSHKeyGenerationStatus.name: agentSSHKeyGenerationStatus
agentSSHKeyGenerationStatus.description: Indicates what key files are currently being generated, if any.

agentSSHRSAKeyControl.name: agentSSHRSAKeyControl
agentSSHRSAKeyControl.description: Controls RSA key generation and deletion. Always returns noop(1).

agentSSHDSAKeyControl.name: agentSSHDSAKeyControl
agentSSHDSAKeyControl.description: Controls DSA key generation and deletion. Always returns noop(1).
